                <fr:route>/complex-0003/</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="Properties of addition of complex numbers">Properties of addition of complex numbers</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>theorem</fr:taxon>
                <fr:meta name="source"><fr:link href="/lankham-2016-linear/" title="Linear algebra as an introduction to abstract mathematics" uri="http://localhost:8000/lankham-2016-linear/" display-uri="lankham-2016-linear" type="local">Linear algebra as an introduction to abstract mathematics</fr:link> Theorem 2.2.4</fr:meta>
                <fr:meta name="source"><fr:link href="/axler-1996-linear/" title="Linear Algebra Done Right" uri="http://localhost:8000/axler-1996-linear/" display-uri="axler-1996-linear" type="local">Linear Algebra Done Right</fr:link> Theorem 1.3</fr:meta>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z_{1},z_{2},z_{3}\in \mathbb {C}]]></fr:tex> be complex numbers. Then the following all hold:</html:p>
                <html:ol><html:li>Associativity: <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(z_{1}+z_{2})+z_{3}=z_{1}+(z_{2}+z_{3})]]></fr:tex></html:li>
<html:li>Commutativity: <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z_{1}+z_{2}=z_{2}+z_{1}]]></fr:tex></html:li>
<html:li>Additive identity: There is a unique complex number denoted <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[0]]></fr:tex> such that for any <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z\in \mathbb {C}]]></fr:tex> we have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[0+z=z]]></fr:tex>. Moreover, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[0=(0,0)]]></fr:tex>.</html:li>
<html:li>Additive inverse: For each <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z\in \mathbb {C}]]></fr:tex> there exists a unique complex number denoted <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[-z]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z+(-z)=0]]></fr:tex>. Moreover, if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z=(x,y)]]></fr:tex>, then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[-z=(-x,-y)]]></fr:tex>.</html:li></html:ol>
              </fr:mainmatter>
