                <fr:title text="Properties of complex conjugation">Properties of complex conjugation</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>theorem</fr:taxon>
                <fr:meta name="source"><fr:link href="/lankham-2016-linear/" title="Linear algebra as an introduction to abstract mathematics" uri="http://localhost:8000/lankham-2016-linear/" display-uri="lankham-2016-linear" type="local">Linear algebra as an introduction to abstract mathematics</fr:link> Theorem 2.2.9</fr:meta>
                <fr:meta name="source"><fr:link href="/axler-1996-linear/" title="Linear Algebra Done Right" uri="http://localhost:8000/axler-1996-linear/" display-uri="axler-1996-linear" type="local">Linear Algebra Done Right</fr:link> Theorem 4.4</fr:meta>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z_{1}]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z_{2}\in \mathbb {C}]]></fr:tex> be complex numbers. Then the following all hold:</html:p>
                <html:ol><html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\overline {z_{1}+z_{2}}=\overline {z_{1}}+\overline {z_{2}}]]></fr:tex> (the conjugate of the sum is the sum of conjugates)</html:li>
<html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\overline {z_{1}z_{2}}=\overline {z_{1}}\overline {z_{2}}]]></fr:tex> (the conjugate of products is the product of conjugates)</html:li>
<html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\overline {1/z_{1}}=1/\overline {z_{1}}]]></fr:tex> when <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[z_{1}\neq 0]]></fr:tex></html:li>
<html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\overline {z_{1}}=z_{1}]]></fr:tex> if and only if <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Im (z_{1})=0]]></fr:tex></html:li>
<html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\overline {\overline {z_{1}}}=z_{1}]]></fr:tex></html:li>
<html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Re (z_{1})=\frac {1}{2}(z_{1}+\overline {z_{1}})]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Im (z_{1})=\frac {1}{2\mathrm {i}}(z_{1}-\overline {z_{1}})]]></fr:tex>.</html:li></html:ol>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
